{"type": "article", "id": 14178, "title": "艺术自行车", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-31T06:58:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000319iBqA4Nf5MW8bFGj2.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tMartone Cycling 公司和零售品牌 Ron Robinson 共同推出了一系列充满艺术气息的自行车，他们邀请了许多艺术家来为自行车设计外观色彩，包括来自洛杉矶的 ToMo, Fallen Fruit, Sket One 以及 Zachary Crane。这些自行车有的呈现彩虹的颜色，有的像是融化的巧克力，有的则遍布绽放的花朵。这些车目前正在 Santa Monica 展出，同时也出售（当然价格不菲），<a href=\"http://martonecycling.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141801JxKulQ9DXnya8VzO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141802prcvjY7hJG4nxOmW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141803hAVmN7cOSia2eD3L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141804AKTvJ4dpg5Be19xL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141805fWELvk5HVJocxR4m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141805AqlvuhmPrDSj50y2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}